articles.title: Experts give up hope for 157 false killer whales stranded on a beach in Australia's Tasmania state - The Associated Press
articles.description: Marine experts have given up hope of rescuing more than 150 false killer whales that stranded on a remote beach on Australia’s island state of Tasmania. Experts including veterinarians were at the scene on Wednesday near Arthur River on Tasmania’s northwest c…
